  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "However, measuring creativity in essay writing evaluation is a challenging task.",
    "The evaluation metric for creativity encompasses attributes such as fluency, flexibility, original-ity, elaboration, and appropriateness (Lee et al. 2023), which are difficult to quantify.",
    "Only a few studies have explored creative writing in AES tasks, particularly utilizing deep learning methods (Liang et al. 2021; Zhang et al. 2022; Lee et al. 2023).",
    "Hence, we propose that investigating creativity within the context of AES would be an intriguing research direction.",
    "One of the challenges in AES is effectively capturing adversarially crafted essay inputs, such as those with grammatically correct sentences but poor coherence, or even AI generated essays."
  ],
